<p>We know this method: we get or create the Stripe Customer, create InvoiceItems
for any products, create the Subscription, and then create an invoice, if needed.</p>
<p>Before adding the invoice items, let's add the coupon to the Customer. So, if
<code>$cart-&gt;getCouponCodeValue()</code>, then very simply,
<code>$stripeCustomer-&gt;coupon = $cart-&gt;getCouponCode()</code>. Make it official with <code>$customer-&gt;save()</code>:</p>
